With some other cuts, it fits!

  

However, the cutting bit on the Dremel was not long enough to go all the way though the toolbox, so I finished off with a jigsaw. 

  

[![](http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-QFdWkQUB_OI/Ush8KgOmTyI/AAAAAAAARkQ/IDMr8X_BmNA/s400/IMAG1545.jpg)](http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-QFdWkQUB_OI/Ush8KgOmTyI/AAAAAAAARkQ/IDMr8X_BmNA/s1600/IMAG1545.jpg)

